>Description:
Following the lead of other html browsers, it would be
convenient if the Help Desk web pane would interpret
spacebar as "show me the next page of content"
>How-To-Repeat:
bring up the help desk
search for "do"
click in the search results pane
press the space bar

rather than doing nothing, I'm suggesting that the page should scroll
